bridge
Interface NativeServerSocket

All Superinterfaces:
NativeInterface
All Known Implementing Classes:
NativeServerSocketImpl
public interface NativeServerSocket
extends NativeInterface

this implements server socket "accept", used for the simulator and android the key to making this work is that it also implements the I/O for the underlying sockets. All the methods return integers, which if < -1 are error codes that should be re-thrown as IOException errors.

Ddyer
